## Pre-made Decks

``` elisp
;; claude code facts decks
(defun my/drill-claude-code-facts ()
  (interactive)
  (my/org-drill-by-tags "+claude_code+_fact"))

;; kubernetes deck
(defun my/drill-kubernetes ()
  (interactive)
  (my/org-drill-by-tags "+kubernetes"))
```

